come, have you?

3
00:00:41,166 --> 00:00:43,916
I've been expecting you.
Welcome to the party.

4
00:00:47,291 --> 00:00:48,625
Eu!

5
00:00:48,708 --> 00:00:53,375
Wow, I can feel your
power from here. What a rush!

6
00:00:59,458 --> 00:01:02,000
You're even stronger
than I thought!

7
00:01:05,541 --> 00:01:07,958
But even the strong
can be brought down.

8
00:01:08,041 --> 00:01:10,541
So let's see how
you fare against this.

9
00:01:26,833 --> 00:01:28,125
No, don't?

10
00:03:26,041 --> 00:03:28,333
Whoa, she's using Mystletainn?

11
00:03:28,416 --> 00:03:30,291
Lady Hellscythe.

12
00:03:30,375 --> 00:03:32,500
