starting to make sense.

13
00:03:32,583 --> 00:03:36,125
This must be why I was
able to absorb Haruna's powers.

14
00:03:36,208 --> 00:03:37,666
Hey, stop gawking
at me, you pervert,

15
00:03:37,750 --> 00:03:39,375
