my powers immediately!

16
00:03:39,458 --> 00:03:40,166
This instant!

17
00:03:40,250 --> 00:03:41,500
And not just that.

18
00:03:42,541 --> 00:03:44,250
I came here
because I was drawn by

19
00:03:44,333 --> 00:03:46,291
the power of a
Magical Garment Girl.

20
00:03:46,375 --> 00:03:48,875
But also why Megalos
are being drawn to me.

21
00:03:48,958 --> 00:03:52,166
