over your own realm instead?

27
00:04:09,958 --> 00:04:13,083
You've grown attached to that
undead pervert, haven't you?

28
00:04:13,166 --> 00:04:16,000
Wasting magic of your
magnitude is a shame.

29
00:04:16,083 --> 00:04:18,666
