seem to have any use for it,

30
00:04:18,750 --> 00:04:22,125
then I think it's only fitting
that I take it all from you!

31
00:04:28,500 --> 00:04:33,416
Oh yeah. I'm gonna love having
that kind of magic inside me!

32
00:04:33,500 --> 00:04:34,958
