33
00:04:43,500 --> 00:04:44,750
Neckwear-mancer!

34
00:04:45,583 --> 00:04:47,083
Eu.

35
00:04:56,375 --> 00:04:57,666
How touching.

36
00:04:57,750 --> 00:05:00,541
You're trying to protect
your pitiful little friends.

37
00:05:02,500 --> 00:05:05,958
How human! Oh, and
speaking of which.

38
00:05:06,041 --> 00:05:08,166
Did you know that human beings
have a limit on the percent

39
00:05:08,250 --> 00:05:10,333
of strength their
bodies can use?

40
00:05:10,416 --> 00:05:12,666
But for someone like me,
who has a stock of lives,

41
00:05:12,750 --> 00:05:17,166
