One hundred percent!

42
00:05:18,208 --> 00:05:22,291
One hundred and fifty percent!
Two hundred percent!

43
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:29,125
Three hundred percent!

44
00:05:30,416 --> 00:05:34,208
Four hundred! Five hundred!

45
00:05:40,208 --> 00:05:41,666
She's strong.

46
00:05:41,750 --> 00:05:46,000
Yes. But what makes Lady
Hellscythe truly powerful?

47
00:05:47,333 --> 00:05:49,916
Would you please
just fall over already?

48
00:05:53,875 --> 00:05:56,625
No! Not yet!

49
00:05:57,458 --> 00:06:00,625
It's neither her
armor, nor her magic...

50
00:06:10,250 --> 00:06:12,708
