utter a single word.

53
00:06:18,541 --> 00:06:22,000
Just one word from her,
and someone'll die?

54
00:06:22,083 --> 00:06:23,583
Then drop dead!

55
00:06:28,416 --> 00:06:29,583
Yeah, of course.

56
00:06:30,333 --> 00:06:32,625
That why she's
sealed away her powers.

57
00:06:32,708 --> 00:06:35,916
If she didn't restrain herself,
she could kill someone.

58
00:06:46,291 --> 00:06:48,125
Based on what she
told me, she feels pain

59
00:06:48,208 --> 00:06:52,500
