61
00:07:17,750 --> 00:07:19,666
She feels the pain of
others when they die,

62
00:07:19,750 --> 00:07:22,416
and she's feeling it
with Kyoko right now.

63
00:07:22,875 --> 00:07:24,541
To protect us.

64
00:07:47,291 --> 00:07:50,166
Your words can't affect me
if I can't hear any of them.

65
00:07:52,250 --> 00:07:55,583
Just as I expected,
you're incredibly powerful.

66
00:07:55,666 --> 00:07:58,291
But not nearly
enough to stop me.

67
00:07:58,916 --> 00:08:00,333
Get out of there!

68
00:08:00,416 --> 00:08:03,083
Total magic power, release!

69
00:08:12,541 --> 00:08:13,958
Eu!

70
00:08:24,875 --> 00:08:28,625
How ironic. Over and over
she kept saying "die"

71
00:08:28,708 --> 00:08:31,750
but it looks like she's
the one who's life has ended.

72
00:08:31,833 --> 00:08:36,083
No coming back now or ever.

73
00:08:39,583 --> 00:08:41,041
Ya know, usually
when I see someone

