But something's weird this time.

76
00:08:46,916 --> 00:08:49,791
Seeing what that girl is
doing to the neckwear-mancer.

77
00:08:49,875 --> 00:08:52,708
It's making me get
really freakin' angry.

78
00:08:52,791 --> 00:08:57,916
And the only thing I wanna do
is kick that blonde chick's ass!

79
00:08:58,000 --> 00:09:00,083
Good, because I think that's
exactly what we're gonna have

80
00:09:00,166 --> 00:09:03,125
