make it outta this in one piece.

81
00:09:03,208 --> 00:09:06,166
You're right.
So let's do it then.

82
00:09:06,250 --> 00:09:08,416
Ayumu. I just thought
up a new technique

83
00:09:08,500 --> 00:09:10,833
that may prove to
be our finishing blow.

84
00:09:10,916 --> 00:09:12,416
When we get back
to the house later,

85
00:09:12,500 --> 00:09:15,375
