me think up a name for it.

86
00:09:17,208 --> 00:09:19,291
Eu put her life
on the line for us,

87
00:09:19,375 --> 00:09:21,500
so we've gotta
do the same for her.

88
00:09:22,916 --> 00:09:24,208
Let's go.

89
00:09:28,541 --> 00:09:30,083
New strike.

90
00:09:31,458 --> 00:09:34,250
Name to be decided!

91
00:09:48,958 --> 00:09:51,166
Eat this, blondie!

92
00:10:01,291 --> 00:10:02,250
Haruna!

93
00:10:06,416 --> 00:10:09,291
You have to get back up
before she can strike again!

94
00:10:18,541 --> 00:10:20,458
What the? Is she nuts?

95
00:10:53,833 --> 00:10:56,083
Ah! That feels better.

96
